{"id":646255,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/【立此存照】郝海东发布严重错误言论遭遇全/","date":"2020-06-04T09:37:21Z","modified":"2020-06-05T01:15:20Z","title":"【立此存照】郝海东发布“严重错误言论”遭遇全网封杀","content":"<p>北京时间6月4日，前中国足球名将郝海东在郭文贵、班农等人主导的“新中国联邦”建国行动中以“中文宣讲人”身份出镜，宣读了近半小时的“新中国联邦宣言”，郝海东的妻子叶钊颖也在节目中现身。</p>\n<p>郝海东宣读“新中国联邦”建国宣言</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"六月三日 郝海东建国宣言\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oIs1tcWZtGU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"郝海东 叶钊颖夫妇 齐发声 20200603\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q-Wf_xfcNB8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>郝海东“宣言”内容发布后不久，其微博<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/haohaidong0509\">个人账号</a>即遭封锁，在被封之前微博粉丝数量接近770万。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646385\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-300x209.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-300x209.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-1024x715.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-768x536.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-1536x1072.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-2048x1429.jpeg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东1-2-1080x754.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646257\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1.png 1932w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1-300x159.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1-1024x542.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1-768x406.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1-1536x813.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东-1-1080x571.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a>在新浪微博搜索“郝海东”反馈的所有结果，相关评论功能均被关闭。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646258\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2.png 1376w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2-300x211.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2-1024x722.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2-768x541.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东2-1080x761.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646259\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"153\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3.png 1270w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3-300x92.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3-1024x313.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3-768x235.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东3-1080x330.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>目前，与“郝海东”及家人相关的国内媒体报道，正大量被删除，疑似有统一的官方指令下达。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646261\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4.png 1408w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4-300x289.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4-1024x986.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4-768x740.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/郝海东4-1080x1040.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>体坛周报发布声明严厉谴责郝海东的“错误言论”，并宣布停止对郝海东的一切报道。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646262\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"931\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image.png 1078w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image-145x300.png 145w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image-495x1024.png 495w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image-768x1589.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image-743x1536.png 743w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/image-990x2048.png 990w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38912,39486,39270],"tags":[9249,9241,22995,9283,40742,40377,26519]}